{"tid":734140,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我老婆今日去沙灘游水，比班麻甩佬睇蝕哂。。。","createTime":"2018-07-08T11:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T14:19:34.000Z","uid":86587,"like":2,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"897b9efcc552e7d4359bb29f6de0db1bb4d639fd","tid":734140,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"話說我出年就要考DSE，我老婆日日同我一齊溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201602/065afb905b1a75b6174c11dc286d3e51.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201602%2F065afb905b1a75b6174c11dc286d3e51.JPG&h=23bf825f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢見我溫得咁攰，於是特登買咗件好性感嘅泳衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住同我一齊去沙灘游水<img src=\"https://img.moegirl.org/common/thumb/9/9d/Kotegawa_yui.png/400px-Kotegawa_yui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.moegirl.org%2Fcommon%2Fthumb%2F9%2F9d%2FKotegawa_yui.png%2F400px-Kotegawa_yui.png&h=96b35086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知去到沙灘，見到好多麻甩佬對我老婆眼甘甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20140826/photo/bkn-20140826105527656-0826_00822_001_02p.jpg?20140826120033\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140826105527656-0826_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20140826120033&h=446e7a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老婆依家匿埋喺屋企唔敢見人，我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180619/0a5dd07a276045beb9758bc4d96b01ae.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180619%2F0a5dd07a276045beb9758bc4d96b01ae.jpeg&h=710d4b9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d77cd4cef48e80e111c39fc6945b4760210b733","tid":734140,"uid":16